
Please read the release notes contained in the file

   RELEASE.html

to learn about recent changes, what you will have to do to
upgrade from a previous version, and new features.

The README.html contains install and compile instructions, an 
overview, credits, and other information.

Check the file docs/License.html for information on license issues.

The documentation, essentially a copy of the website, is
in the docs subdirectory. 

Please subscribe to the WebMacro mailing list:

  webmacro-request@webmacro.org

Let us know what you think, whether you have any problems, and how
we can improve WebMacro!

-Justin



